			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong>Audio Sermon by: Pastor George Hillman</strong></p>
<p><strong>Text: John 16:1-7</strong></p>
<p>Many times Jesus makes reference to one whom He will send when He departs. In this study we take a look at who the Holy Spirit is and what He does.</p>
